PrecisApproval of the reappointment by the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans of JOHN WOOD of Sarnia, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a successor is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective August 26, 2016.
